  "title": "Climate Indices — South America",
  "uid": "climate-indices-sa",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "1h",
  "time": { "from": "1990-01-01T00:00:00Z", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {},
  "panels": [

    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "About this dashboard",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 3 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Climate Indices — South America\nLarge-scale climate oscillations shape rainfall, temperature, and extreme events across Latin America. This dashboard tracks the main indices updated daily from public sources (NOAA CPC / PSL). **ONI/Niño 3.4**: El Niño–Southern Oscillation — warm events (>+0.5 °C) bring drought to NE Brazil and floods in SE South America. **MEI**: multivariate ENSO index. **SAM**: Southern Annular Mode — positive phase strengthens the westerlies. **IOD**: Indian Ocean Dipole — influences Atlantic teleconnections."
      },
      "datasource": null
    },

    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "ONI (latest)",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 3, "w": 4, "h": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "°C",
          "decimals": 2,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "blue",  "value": null },
              { "color": "blue",  "value": -2.0 },
              { "color": "#6baed6","value": -0.5 },
              { "color": "green", "value": 0.5 },
              { "color": "orange","value": 1.0 },
              { "color": "red",   "value": 1.5 }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": []
        }
      },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "orientation": "auto", "textMode": "auto", "colorMode": "background" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource", "uid": "${DS_INFINITY}" },
          "refId": "A",
          "type": "csv",
          "source": "url",
          "url": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dbrisaro/climate-dashboard/main/data/oni.csv",
          "parser": "backend",
          "columns": [
            { "selector": "date", "text": "date", "type": "timestamp" },
            { "selector": "oni",  "text": "oni",  "type": "number" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },

